Notes:

1. The above statement should be read with the notes on adjustments for the Restated Consolidated Summary Statement of the Assets and Liabilities, the Restated Consolidated Summary Statement of Profit and Loss and the Restated Consolidated Summary of Cash Flows as appearing in annexure I to III and significant accounting policies and other notes as appearing in -annexure IV and V.

